民警感染治愈后再请战，“申请感染风险最高的任务”。
After the police infection cured, please fight, "to apply for the highest risk of infection tasks."
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 邵克 通讯员 祝赟2月18日，湖北孝感汉川市公安局党组收到一份特殊的“请战书”：“我是一名刚刚康复的新冠肺炎患者……我向市局党组申请参与此次抗击新冠肺炎感染风险最高的任务。
Shao Kai Correspondent Zhu Kai-yun February 18, Hubei Xiaoyan Hanchuan City Public Security Bureau received a special "invitation letter": "I am a newly recovered patients... I applied to the municipal party group to participate in the fight against the highest risk of New Crown Pneumonia.
”递交这份请战书的是汉川市公安局网安大队民警吴华东，2月15日，他刚刚战胜新冠病毒，康复出院。
The application was submitted by Wu Huadong, a police officer of the Hanchuan Public Security Bureau who had just recovered from the Novovirus on February 15.
吴华东递交的请战书。
Application from Wu Huadong.
本文图片均汉川警方供图2020年1月23日以来，汉川市公安局全警参与疫情防控的阻击战，作为奋战防控一线的队伍，其中也有人不幸感染新冠病毒。
Since Jan. 23, 2020, all police officers of the Hanchuan Public Security Bureau have taken part in the fight against the disease, and some of them have been infected with the new crown virus.
1月27日，刚刚完成值守任务的汉吴华东开始出现低烧的症状。
On January 27, just finished his duty, Han Wu East China began to develop symptoms of low fever.
吴华东第一时间主动向汉川市公安局报告情况，并自行隔离。
Wu Huadong first took the initiative to report the situation to the Hanchuan Public Security Bureau and isolated himself.
同时，近期与吴华东有过接触的同事按要求隔离观察。
At the same time, the recent contact with Wu Huadong colleagues on the requirements of isolation observation.
2月2日，在经过连续发烧五日后，吴华东出现多项疑似感染新冠病毒的症状，吴华东到医院进行检查，CT显示他的肺部呈毛玻璃样，经过核酸检测之后，被确诊感染上冠状病毒，并被隔离治疗。
On February 2, after a series of fever for five days, Wu Huadong developed symptoms of a suspected new crown virus. Wu Huadong went to the hospital for a check-up. CT showed that his lungs were glassy-like. After DNA testing, he was diagnosed with coronavirus and was treated in isolation.
根据吴华东回想，最有可能的感染时间应该是1月16日。
According to Wu Huadong's recollection, the most likely infection time should be January 16.
当日，吴华东因其他病症到武汉协和医院检查，在医院未戴口罩的情况下待了半天时间。
On that day, Wu Huadong because of other diseases to Wuhan Concord hospital inspection, in the hospital did not wear a mask for half a day.
当得知自己感染了新冠肺炎后，吴华东坦诚，当时的心理压力非常大，一是担心病毒传染给家人、同事以及其他人。
When he learned that he was infected with pneumonia, Wu Huadong confessed that the psychological pressure was very high, one is worried about the virus to their families, colleagues and others.
毕竟因为自己的原因，多名朝夕相处的战友和家人都已经被隔离；二是害怕病情出现严重的后果。
After all, for reasons of their own, many of their comrades-in-arms and family have been quarantined; second, they fear serious consequences.
在医院住院期间，亲人、同事以及医护人员的鼓励给了吴华东与病毒抗争的勇气，汉川市公安局分管局领导每天都会给吴华东打电话，询问病情，坚定他战胜病毒的信心。
During his stay in hospital, the encouragement of relatives, colleagues and medical staff gave Wu Huadong the courage to fight the virus. Every day, the head of the branch bureau of the Hanchuan Public Security Bureau called Wu Huadong to enquire about his condition and strengthen his confidence in overcoming the virus.
“既然已经感染了，只能正确面对它。
"Now that I'm infected, I can only face it correctly.
积极的配合医生治疗，保持乐观向上的心态，争取早日康复，不做这场战役的‘逃兵’”吴华东给自己打气。
Actively cooperates with the doctor treatment, maintains the optimistic upward mentality, strives for the quick recovery, does not do this battle 'deserter' Wu Huadong gives the self-encouragement.
工作中的吴华东（左一）。
Wu Huadong at work (1st left).
经过几天的治疗，2月5日，吴华东身体明显好转，已经停止发烧。
After several days of treatment, Wu Huadong improved markedly on February 5 and has stopped running a fever.
2月7日，第二次检查结果呈阴性，2月9日，第三次检查，结果继续呈阴性。
On 7 February, the second test was negative, and on 9 February, the third, the results continued to be negative.
2月15日，经过医院专家的判断，吴华东已经康复痊愈，能够出院。
Feb. 15, after a hospital expert judgement, Wu Huadong has recovered and can be discharged.
与此同时，好消息也接连不断，与吴华东有过密切接触的家人、同事，经过14天的隔离观察后，均未出现疑似感染的症状，一切正常。
Meanwhile, the good news has continued, with close contact with Wu Huadong's family, colleagues, after 14 days of isolation observation, no suspected symptoms of infection, all normal.
在经过几天的居家观察后，吴华东确定已经完全康复，2月18日，他主动联系汉川市公安局党组，递交请战书。
After several days of home observation, Wu Huadong is sure to be fully recovered. On Feb. 18, he contacted the Hanchuan Public Security Bureau to submit an application.
在请战书中，吴华东写道：“我是新冠肺炎康复群体，体内短期内有针对新冠肺炎的抗体，能抵御新冠肺炎感染……我坚决请战，哪里情况最紧急、哪里风险最高，我都愿意冲锋在前，绝不后退。
In his battle petition, Wu Huadong wrote: "I am the new crown pneumonia convalescent group, the body short-term against the new crown pneumonia, can resist the infection of the new crown pneumonia... I firmly request war, where the most urgent, where the highest risk, I am willing to march ahead, never retreat.
”本期编辑 邢潭推荐阅读。
Xing Tam, editor of this issue, recommends reading.
